{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So, you're plunging into a world where our bad-ass, ghost-busting squad (also known as S.P.A.T.) slays night creeps that will probably give you nightmares. You\u2019ll need to be sharp and fast to outsmart and defeat these freaky creatures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, it's clear as day: we tackle eerie critters like Bigfoot, Twilight wannabes (werewolves), mythical cannibals (wendigos), broomstick-riders (witches), and a whole festival of horror. Get ready for some gnarly weapon customization, a chilling vibe, some random scares, and a pinch of naughty humor that will tickle your funny bone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customizable Arsenal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/arsenal1.gif?t=1736329734\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gear up with a ton of guns and cool gadgets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Boost up those weapons as per your gaming style and also try messing around with spooky attachments to ace the fight against these monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Spooky Storytime</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/lore1.gif?t=1736329734\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to untangle creepy local legends and confront horrific nightmares from urban myths. Even if you're armed to your teeth, can you handle the chills going down your spine? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Watch out for four monster-bosses hiding in the dark and a big nasty mob of eerie beasts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Brutal Buddy Action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/coop1.gif?t=1736329734\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Raise hell with your squad of an elite team in our adrenaline-spiking co-op mode! Strategize your attacks, cover for each other, and rain down a symphony of destruction on those freaky monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember, in SPAT's universe, working together is your golden ticket to survival - and there's nothing like beating down horror movie rejects with your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Black Comedy &amp; Chills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/scrim1.gif?t=1736329734\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for a nerve-racking journey loaded with dark humor and the odd jump-scare. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to laugh at the madness, but remember, it's a thin line between giggles and screams in this unsettling world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">So why wait? Join Those Who are Already Fighting Monsters!</h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Blood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1565660/b455c869f254ac03fb64f4e48dc69f1afe72d23f.jpg"},{"name":"Lycanthrope's Bane","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1565660/772774fccbb4ab54439be757e04f7e71ea078b3d.jpg"},{"name":"Yeti Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1565660/7e90eddfe46c80a22f844ad6469e4c448bf890d7.jpg"},{"name":"Witch Hunt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1565660/6920169eb5462b57032667cae578636952ef5b0e.jpg"},{"name":"Wendigo's End","path":"https:/